I am using a Field Group with 3 object counts to collect text content and a datetime field to choose when that content will display. The issue I have is that when I loop though the 3 Field Groups, only that loop's datetime fields are collected, plus the datetime fields that were previously collected, but the 1st loop needs the 2nd datetime and the 2nd loop also needs the 3rd loop's datetime.

```{% set today = unixtimestamp( today() ) %}

 {% for item in module.row %}
 {% if loop.index == '1' %}
 {% set hotelDate1 = item.datetime_field|unixtimestamp %}
{% elif loop.index == '2' %}
{% set hotelDate2 = item.datetime_field|unixtimestamp %}
 {% elif loop.index == '3' %}
 {% set hotelDate3 = item.datetime_field|unixtimestamp %}
{% endif %}

 {% if today &gt;= hotelDate1 and today &lt; hotelDate2 %}
show content 1
{% elif today &gt;= hotelDate2 and today &lt; hotelDate3 %}
show content 2
{% elif today &gt;= hoteldate3 %}
show content 3
{% endif %}```
